BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:censusday-2030@civic
SUMMARY:Census Day
DESCRIPTION:April 1 is the official reference date for the U.S. Census\, conducted every ten years as required by the Constitution. All residents are asked to report their status as of this date. Census data shapes congressional representation and federal funding for the next decade.
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20300401
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20300402
END:VEVENT

